item.title: CVE-2021-24600|2024-08-03T19:35:20.289Z -- unknown -- wp%20dialog
item.description: The WP Dialog WordPress plugin through 1.2.5.5 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings before outputting them in pages, allowing high privilege users to perform Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed.
